name: TocoDeco's Echidna
description:
She may not be able to pronounce 'echidna,' but she knows it's a monotreme, and that the platypus can swim and is also a monotreme. 
Thanks to @TocoDeco for producing this artwork. One third of the profits will go towards saving Australian wildlife. 
This piece was produced for the NFT Neighbourhood podcast and is the first piece in the series.

Thanks Toco for indulging me and encouraging me on this project.
- Mr Neighbourhood
